                "html": "<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">（抄自抄自<span class=\"footnote-word\" style=\"color: rgb(30, 107, 184); font-weight: bold;\">乾隆丁未本</span><sup class=\"footnote-ref\" style=\"line-height: 0; color: rgb(30, 107, 184); font-weight: bold;\">[1]</sup>，殘1卷，2024-4-13）</p> \n<blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: left; background-position-y: top; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">嘉靖壬子(嘉靖31年），邑侯<span class=\"footnote-word\" style=\"color: rgb(30, 107, 184); font-weight: bold;\">韓叔陽</span><sup class=\"footnote-ref\" style=\"line-height: 0; color: rgb(30, 107, 184); font-weight: bold;\">[2]</sup>大造賦役黃冊，聽信靈泉鄉豪右朱文經，更改七鄉輸糧科則，重加政內鄉額米七百余石。府主洪公諧力主新法苛征，民不勝害。公念奔告水程具疏赴奏。其疏曰：</p> \n</blockquote> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">浙江等處承宣佈政司使金華府浦江縣儒學廩生臣陳九經，奏為奸豪蠱 政亂法更制酷害蒼生事。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">臣聞夏禹鑄九鼎以分九州，則壤成賦不以一例病民。降及商周，鄉遂都鄙，隨其地土所宜，以定公田祿養，正其經界，不致豪強之兼并，不為貪暴之多取，循古典也，何事於紛更哉？</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\"><span class=\"footnote-word\" style=\"color: rgb(30, 107, 184); font-weight: bold;\">商君</span><sup class=\"footnote-ref\" style=\"line-height: 0; color: rgb(30, 107, 184); font-weight: bold;\">[3]</sup>開阡陌以反古，恣慘毒以亂秦，道途側目、閉口含冤，更法何利於國家哉？漢唐宋曆遵舊籍，雖加損益，不過因時制宜，期與百姓相安而已，並不紛更田制，以拂民情。間有王安石突創青苗法，圖為興利，詎知反害我蒼生。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">我太祖高皇帝，軫念民隱，以賦稅為國家重務、錢糧乃下民膏血，關係匪輕，不許亂行更變。戶部鑄銅版以定科則糧長，給勘合以禁奸貪，其為國計慮者至深切矣。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\"><a href=\"%E6%8C%87%E8%98%87%E5%B7%9E%E5%BA%9C%E5%92%8C%E6%9D%BE%E6%B1%9F%E5%BA%9C%22%E8%98%87%E6%9D%BE%22\" style=\"color: rgb(30, 107, 184); font-weight: bold; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; text-decoration-style: solid; text-decoration-color: currentcolor; text-decoration-thickness: auto; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">蘇松</a>等府，原因富戶資助張士誠，負固不服，故照其租簿之額數，以定稅糧之規則，征之太重，洪武十三年加恩存恤，特命戶部為之遞減，其為民情計者，誠優渥矣。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">浙東山郡，僻在一隅，田有水平高，地有上中下。洪武七年，命<span class=\"footnote-word\" style=\"color: rgb(30, 107, 184); font-weight: bold;\">信國公</span><sup class=\"footnote-ref\" style=\"line-height: 0; color: rgb(30, 107, 184); font-weight: bold;\">[4]</sup>延坵履畞，相土定糧，皆因循古制隨在宜民。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">本邑靈泉鄉，附郭平陽曠原沃野，土厚租多，水田每畆科糧四升四合，比之浙西四斗科徵者為尤輕矣；政內鄉叠嶂層巒、山高水冷，其土薄而租微，水田每畞科糧一升九合，比之青田三合科徵者為尤重矣。因土之厚簿以定糧之輕重，祖宗成法萬古良規。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">豪右鼓惑縣官積奸乘機射利。一旦更變舊制，不論地利厚薄，槩以一例取盈，每畞併科三升二合，巨屨小屨同價，是亂天下也，何利於生民哉？</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">赴愬者坐獄，訟獄者連刑，坑戮儒生，荼毒良善，是害百姓也，何取於新法哉？</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">民困征誅，望風逃竄，山鄉竟為廢土，額糧何所充納，征役何所征輸，其為利害何如哉。更新變舊，又非額外加增，平糧何益於國，不平何損於國，其為是非何如哉。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">乞勅都察院轉行撫按勘問，遵成法以安民，懲奸豪而順治，超拔無辜，申明公道。為此具本親賫奏聞。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">嘉靖三十六年二月具疏。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">蒙恩准奏，命下於嘉靖三十六年五月，奉旨欽差戶部臨省。</p> \n<figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;\"> \n <img src=\"https://files.mdnice.com/user/38480/1c35c600-6d3a-4583-ab61-bbc1ef1e980c.jpg\" alt=\"乾隆丁未本影印件1\" style=\"display: block; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; object-fit: fill; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"> \n <figcaption style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: center; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n   乾隆丁未本影印件1 \n </fi